    "content_html": "<div class=\"news-content article-content\" id=\"\" style=\"position:relative\"><div class=\"news-content-parsed\"><p>外盘方面，美伊谈判结果不合预期，市场担忧情绪上升，另美国近期降雨影响<span><a class=\"link-wrapper link-blue\" href=\"https://q.10jqka.com.cn/thshy/detail/code/885811\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" style=\"word-break:break-all;cursor:pointer;color:#36F\" target=\"_blank\">玉米（885811）</a></span>播种，支撑美<span><a class=\"link-wrapper link-blue\" href=\"https://q.10jqka.com.cn/thshy/detail/code/885811\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" style=\"word-break:break-all;cursor:pointer;color:#36F\" target=\"_blank\">玉米（885811）</a></span>价格；USDA4月供需报告利空，美<span><a class=\"link-wrapper link-blue\" href=\"https://q.10jqka.com.cn/thshy/detail/code/885811\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" style=\"word-break:break-all;cursor:pointer;color:#36F\" target=\"_blank\">玉米（885811）</a></span>承压。</p><p>国内方面，上周<span><a class=\"link-wrapper link-blue\" href=\"https://q.10jqka.com.cn/thshy/detail/code/885811\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" style=\"word-break:break-all;cursor:pointer;color:#36F\" target=\"_blank\">玉米（885811）</a></span>07合约窄幅震荡。基本面看，国内<span><a class=\"link-wrapper link-blue\" href=\"https://q.10jqka.com.cn/thshy/detail/code/885811\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" style=\"word-break:break-all;cursor:pointer;color:#36F\" target=\"_blank\">玉米（885811）</a></span>市场购销逐步活跃，而随着气温回升，且农户存在回款需求，农户售粮进度加快，叠加小麦抛储替代，<span><a class=\"link-wrapper link-blue\" href=\"https://q.10jqka.com.cn/thshy/detail/code/885811\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" style=\"word-break:break-all;cursor:pointer;color:#36F\" target=\"_blank\">玉米（885811）</a></span>现货上涨动能减弱。不过港口库存有限，下游企业库存总体低位，对<span><a class=\"link-wrapper link-blue\" href=\"https://q.10jqka.com.cn/thshy/detail/code/885811\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" style=\"word-break:break-all;cursor:pointer;color:#36F\" target=\"_blank\">玉米（885811）</a></span>形成支撑。</p></div></div>",
